{"tid":96013,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死2隻]哈綏高速至少40車連環相撞　大雪肇禍5死傷","createTime":"2017-01-26T13:11:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-29T06:31:25.000Z","uid":32407,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3436dcf96ed2d856ac96ccefd6d6fcc4bf158b58","tid":96013,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T13:11:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170126/bkncn-20170126144549340-0126_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170126%2Fbkncn-20170126144549340-0126_05011_001.html&d=fItlN44NZXBL7lJw5Qix1GN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=e847b6d9\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170126/bkncn-20170126144549340-0126_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170126/photo/bkncn-20170126144549340-0126_05011_001_01b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170126%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170126144549340-0126_05011_001_01b.jpg&h=accb3457&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n春節臨近，內地不少民眾駕車回鄉過年，惟黑龍江受大雪天氣影響，地面濕滑，能見度低，哈大高速（哈爾濱至綏化）374公里至378公里處，往綏化方向今日下午12時45分發生40至50輛車連環相撞事故，導致雙向行車線完全擠塞，現場有人受傷。據哈爾濱巴彥縣政府最新消息，意外已造成2人死亡，3人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n從網傳影片可見，事故現場一片混亂，部分車輛損毀嚴重，有傷者躺在地上等待救援；雪地上染有血漬，網絡更有傳意外涉及近百車輛。據交警部門的消息，目前哈大高速已全線恢復正常通行，限速每小時60公里。<br />\n<br />\n過唔到年 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69f090a1a0c9708510a9a72b85a0f58ae284ee77","tid":96013,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T13:12:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5e463d4eef91716cdc57038466fa5e7900e2f01","tid":96013,"uid":25221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T06:31:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}